item.title: Alexandre Castelnau
item.description: Hi everyone, my name is Alexandre Castelnau. I am a French graduate student enrolled in a dual degree program between Georgia Tech and CentraleSupélec, graduate engineering school of the Université Paris-Saclay.

item.title: Mrinal Mathur
item.description: I am a Research assistant at TreNDs. I work on building novel research prototypes at the intersection of computer vision, natural language, and Reinforcement Learning. I was also Teaching assistant and co-tutor for Intro to Deep Learning 6851 (Spring Semester 2022)

item.title: Farfalla Hu
item.description: Hi, everyone. My name is Farfalla Hu. I am a multimedia designer and I studied Motion Media and Interactive Design as my undergrad at SCAD. My master’s degree is at GSU in Computer Science.
